\item\label{conf:squareplusc3} A bad 3-face $xyz$ and a normal 4-face $wuvx$ where $d(x)=4$ and $x$ is the only high vertex incident to the 4-face.

\item\label{conf:c3c3} Two 3-faces $xyz$ and $xuv$ where $d(x)=4$ and $d(y) = d(v) = 3$.

